<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Cozen" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Cozen,</orth> to cheat; 1) intr.: <cit><quote>a --ing quean,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.180" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 2, 180</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ing hope,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 2.2.69" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 2, 69</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>some cogging, --ing slave,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 4.2.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 2, 132</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) trans.: <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 95</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 95</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.218" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 218</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.2.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 2, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.170" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 170</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 5.1.40" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.2.76" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 2, 76</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.4.23" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.254" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 254</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.136" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 136</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 77</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.154" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. V, 3, 154</bibl>. With <emph>of,</emph> == to defraud of sth.: <cit><quote>--ing the pillow of a lawful kiss,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 387" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 387</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 38</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.175" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 175</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.5.28" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 5, 28</bibl>.